---
title: Easy Garlic-Herb Chicken & Basil Pesto Risoni Salad with Parmesan
description: Fresh and herby are meeting half way in a salad that’s going to bring peace to your craving for chicken and risonoi. Chicken is
seasoned in herby garlic spices and the risoni is stirred through with soft basil pesto. As a peace offering that will seal the deal,
sprinkle over some Parmesan cheese.
